episodes.title: Prince Andrew Stripped of 'Prince' Title: Royal Scandal Explained | Lorraine
episodes.description:
After weeks of fevered and increasingly lurid revelations and speculation, Buckingham Palace have announced that Prince Andrew will lose his Royal titles and move out of Royal Lodge in Windsor. We will be looking at the latest reaction to this development, and what this means for Andrew's ex-wife Sarah Ferguson, and their two daughters. Former Royal Correspondent Jennie Bond will be exploring the huge historical significance of all of this.
